column5: http://www.fishingtackleshop.com.au/categories/Specials-%26-Clearance/?sort=featured&page=2   I always like a good deal, but I'm unfamiliar with this reel...any feedback.  Holds 14 lbs test, maybe a little to heavy.
Well it`s a salt water reel and it`s coming from Australia, no deals closer to home.

I've used the smaller one's before.  They are a decent reel, made with corrosion resistant parts for saltwater.  They usually go for $150usd, I would assume that shipping from Australia would bump that $75 up to $100 pretty quick.
